jQuery plugin for enabling suggest in select fields.

Tested in FF3.6, Opera10.63, Chrome8.0.552.224 on Linux.

REQUIREMENTS: JQuery.

USAGE:
 <select id="id" ... >
   ...options..
 </select>
 <script>
  $('#id')select_suggest( {...options...} ); 
 </script>

Where options are:
 * limit - maximum number of items to display in suggest.
 * css_class - class of suggest container.
